# Command Line Rules
- Do not use Unix-style command separators like && or ; in commands
- Use separate commands instead of chaining with && or ;
- Commands should be Windows-compatible

# Code Style Rules
- Use TypeScript for all new code
- Follow ESLint and Prettier configurations
- Use ES modules (import/export) not CommonJS (require/module.exports)
- Include proper type definitions
- Follow the monorepo workspace structure